com.collabnet.ccf.core
Class EntityService

java.lang.Object
  com.collabnet.ccf.core.EntityService
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.openadaptor.core.IDataProcessor
public class EntityService
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.openadaptor.core.IDataProcessor

This component will find out whether an artifact coming out of a non-SFEE system has to be created, updated, deleted or ignored within SFEE. It will also try to find out the correct SFEE id for the artifact in question.

Author:
jnicolai
